                                        },
                                        {
                                            "name":  "Kinetic Plating",
                                            "description":  "Generate armor plating that converts a portion of absorbed Kinetic Damage (Physical, \u003cDT_FIRE_COLOR\u003eHeat, \u003cDT_FREEZE_COLOR\u003eCold, and \u003cDT_EXPLOSION_COLOR\u003eBlast) into Energy. Also protects Gauss from being staggered or knocked down. Damage Resistance is relative to the battery level.",
