                                            "description":  "Siphon kinetic energy from the area, charging the battery and inflicting \u003cDT_FREEZE_COLOR\u003eCold Status on nearby enemies. Hold reverses the process, draining the battery and inflicting \u003cDT_FIRE_COLOR\u003eHeat Status on nearby enemies.",
